&nbsp;
Portanto:
&nbsp;
$$d_{\text{afélio}} + d_{\text{periélio}} = 2a \leftrightarrow d_{\text{afélio}} = 2a - d_{\text{periélio}} \to d_{\text{afélio}} = 5,8 - 0,5 = 5,3\ \text{UA}$$

